{wp|monkey}}. It may also involve けっき \'\'kekki\'\' (vigor).\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Fire|type2=Fire\n|ja=バオッキー \'\'Baokkie\'\'|jameaning=From {{tt|爆 \'\'bào\'\'|Chinese for burst/explode}}, {{tt|バースト \'\'bāsuto\'\'|burst}}, and \'\'monkey\'\'. May also involve {{tt|けっき \'\'kekki\'\'|vigor}}.\n|de=Grillchita|demeaning=From \'\'Grill\'\' and \'\'{{wp|Cheeta}}\'\'\n|fr=Flamoutan|frmeaning=From \'\'flame\'\' and \'\'{{tt|orang-outan|orangutan}}\'\'\n|es=Simisear|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|it=Simisear|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=바오키 \'\'Baokkie\'\'|komeaning=Transliteration of Japanese name\n|zh_cmn=爆香猿 \'\'Bàoxiāngyuán\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{wp|Stir frying|{{tt|爆香 \'\'bàoxiāng\'\'|stir-fry}}}} and {{tt|猿 \'\'yuán\'\'|ape}}.\n|ru=Симисир \'\'Simisir\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==Related articles==\n*[[Chili\'s Simisear]]\n*[[Elemental monkeys]]\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Fire}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Fire|prevnum=513|prev=Pansear|nextnum=515|next=Panpour}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Grillchita]]\n[[es:Simisear]]\n[[fr:Flamoutan]]\n[[it:Simisear]]\n[[ja:バオッキー]]\n[[zh:爆香猿]]'}